{"tid":1466462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要繼續和你飛, 但要停止捉鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:43.000Z","uid":164402,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3b465ec3eeabf61b3a43c7f44baec0f7dfb5c5a3","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"其實而家好多人既通病（唔係淨係計示威）都係好短視<br />\n例如佢地發現到公安 唔俾佢走 跟住呢<br />\n無人諗過之後點 淨係諗住而家呢一刻唔俾佢走囉<br />\n記者反而諗多咗一步 就係唔俾公安走 警察就會入嚟救公安<br />\n咁就會攬炒<br />\n結果就真係俾人拉咗三個 又出椒<br />\n議員出嚟叫佢地冷靜唔好打 啲人又鬧議員<br />\n<br />\n劇本已經寫好, 派幾隻鬼入黎, 比人捉到, 就有某d前線仇恨上腦 (我唔理係人定鬼, 影出黎就係入我地數) , 阻/打FA同救護, 係完全中伏"},{"pid":"1d2d49cc03fa37cf923f9bdc8442ae8f0eb22d2d","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:32.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"9f043dae9f917bffe760569fbebca8700f56d48a","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"11cded42c515e187d90fee389200798b4b91c6c7","tid":1466462,"uid":18639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"我明白手足們十分憤怒，但請手足冷靜少少，捉鬼係唔會令我地羸，而係會令我地分化令我地輸。你諗下我地有幾多個手足，你捉到鬼既機率高d定係捉到自己人既機率高d？而就算真係捉到隻鬼，咁之後又有咩野做到？捉鬼重要d定羸返香港重要d？<br />\n本來今日班popo過到黎仲打爆左一個人既頭流哂血，聽朝頭條就係班popo入機場既第一滴血。依家因為捉鬼，仲要捉到果個真係記者黎。雖然佢十分可疑，但事實上佢既身份真係記者。咁聽日既頭條就變左做示威者捉錯記者，完美咁比人spin左風向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔會割蓆 大家共同進退 只係想大家停止捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45711bec29f556f626946389bfa64f2aefc0906b","tid":1466462,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e3db707b7c88fd05efb556d484c6fee0a2afb0","tid":1466462,"uid":180515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"真係唔洗捉鬼，總之唔衝擊，理鳩佢有冇鬼"},{"pid":"7752544cb1adb5c3f1066947335df8936d10fa54","tid":1466462,"uid":48436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6cb1a8908d0a701ebef0e901da21fa1f8ab9cc4","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"160e907e45309b9a3b52034dedfe6048acecf9fe","tid":1466462,"uid":125389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 又係時候提大家點急救<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f186e531b7384bee8abe91d226e685d4d554f1a","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:38.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"82dd27f70849bf0315a5b5b97f5d315e83e26c6a","tid":1466462,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"814 1點"},{"pid":"bfd9530d730c65a524bfc0ecb735b51e14c48388","tid":1466462,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"keep番早幾日咁做就夠架啦"},{"pid":"14b7790689f356ef1f41d2031fd8d93968d1eb8a","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"814058c782a7d22bbc5162745ad1150791ca5b75","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"自推6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73947529c314ce1883c51de454877b8bac065135","tid":1466462,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"自推7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b0f343e295ce43775f24fa326f6b6f98cd83a3","tid":1466462,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"機場 和理非 不阻旅客 不捉鬼 真誠道歉 不忘初心 不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=